        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Below, I'm sharing the best ways to squeeze every drop of value out of monday.com, whether you manage a two-person startup or coordinate campaigns across departments. No fluff, no theory — just practical moves you can make today.",
