      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Boards are the backbone of everything in monday.com. Here's how experienced users set them up for maximum clarity:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. One board per major initiative, not per task.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Your \"Q3 Marketing Campaign\" board should live alongside subitems for email sequences, ad creative, and social posts — all in one place. Splitting these into separate boards creates unnecessary silos.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Use groups as phases or categories.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Each board supports multiple groups (the colored section dividers). I use them to separate project phases — Planning, Execution, Review — so anyone glancing at the board sees progress at a glance.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Pick the right column types.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "monday.com gives you 8 column types in the free plan and more as you upgrade. The ones I lean on most:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Status",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — for tracking where each item stands",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
