      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When your sales team tracks a deal on one board and your delivery team tracks the same client on another, the Mirror column syncs the relevant data between them. No copy-pasting, no stale info.",
