      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where monday.com separates itself from basic to-do apps. The no-code automation builder lets you set triggers and actions without writing a single line of code.",
