          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "monday.com keeps rolling out updates that make the platform more powerful without adding complexity. Here are the ones that caught my attention recently:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Features (from Basic plan and up).",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The new AI capabilities include generating task descriptions, summarizing updates, and even suggesting next steps based on your board data. You get 1,000 AI credits per month starting at the Basic tier, and you can purchase more as needed. For teams drowning in status updates, the AI summary alone is a massive time-saver.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "monday.com Docs.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Think of these as living documents that connect directly to your boards. You write a project brief in a Doc, and the data inside updates in real time as your board changes. No more outdated Word files floating around. The free plan includes up to 3 Docs — enough to test the concept with your team.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real Time Engine.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When you edit a Doc or a board, collaborators see changes instantly. This sounds small until you've experienced the alternative — refreshing a page, wondering if you're looking at the latest version. The real-time sync is buttery smooth.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "200+ Industry-Specific Templates.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Whether you're in construction, education, SaaS, or event planning, there's likely a template built by someone who understands your workflow. These aren't generic placeholders — they include relevant columns, automations, and views tailored to real use cases.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
