      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is monday.com Perfect For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I get asked this a lot: \"Is monday.com right for *my* team?\" Here's my honest take based on who I've seen thrive with it:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Small teams (2-20 people) who need structure but hate complexity.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The free plan supports up to 2 seats with 3 boards. That's enough to manage a couple of core projects and decide if the workflow clicks. For growing teams, plans scale predictably — no surprise price jumps.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Marketing and creative teams.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Campaign tracking, content calendars, asset approvals — monday.com handles all of it beautifully. The visual boards make it easy to see what's in production, what's approved, and what's live.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Agencies managing multiple clients.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Create one board per client. Use groups for project phases. Mirror data between your internal board and the client-facing one. Your clients get transparency; your team gets autonomy.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Operations and HR teams.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Employee onboarding, event logistics, vendor management — the template library covers these workflows out of the box. Custom automations eliminate the repetitive follow-ups that drain ops teams.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Anyone currently juggling spreadsheets.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
