            "text": "Yes. monday.com offers a free forever plan for up to 2 seats with 3 boards, 3 Docs, 200+ templates, 8 column types, and mobile apps. Paid plans start at $9 per seat per month (billed annually) and unlock AI features, more integrations, and additional automations.",
