        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. monday.com was built as a visual alternative to spreadsheet-based project management. It offers real-time collaboration, automated status updates, dashboards, and file attachments — all things spreadsheets either can't do or do poorly.",
